OL,3,CSwansea health board issues highest
OL,4,Calert amid 'exceptionally full'
OL,5,Chospitals
OL,7,FSwansea Bay University Health Board
OL,8,Fhas moved to its highest alert level
OL,9,Famid winter pressures and
OL,10,F"exceptionally full" hospitals.
OL,12,FThe health board declared a business
OL,13,Fcontinuity incident (BCI) on Tuesday,
OL,14,F6 January. It said this would allow
OL,15,Fthem to concentrate resources on
OL,16,Fmaximising patient discharge to create
OL,17,Fadditional bed capacity.
