OL,7,FA spokesperson said the main issue was
OL,8,Fthat hospitals within the health board
OL,9,Farea currently have a number of
OL,10,Fpatients in acute beds who have
OL,11,Fcompleted their treatment and no
OL,12,Flonger need to be in hospital.
OL,13,FHowever, pressures on community
OL,14,Fservices has led to a backlog of
OL,15,Fdischarges.
OL,17,FIt is asking families to "play their
OL,18,Fpart by supporting their loved ones to
OL,19,Fleave hospital if they have been told
OL,20,Fthey are ready to go".
