OL,4,Calert amid 'exceptionally full'
OL,5,Chospitals
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the health board
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are working very closely
OL,9,Fwith our local authority colleagues
OL,10,Fand others to improve this situation,
OL,11,Fbut we are also asking families to
OL,12,Fplay their part by supporting their
OL,13,Floved ones to leave hospital if they
OL,14,Fhave been told they are ready to go.
OL,16,F"They'll not only be helping us to
OL,17,Fprovide timely care to those patients
OL,18,Fwho are waiting for a bed, but also
OL,19,Fhelping their loved ones to recover
OL,20,Fbetter.
