OL,7,F"Hospital's the best place to be for
OL,8,Fanyone needing acute care following a
OL,9,Fserious illness, injury or surgery.
OL,10,FBut staying in an acute care bed once
OL,11,Ftreatment is complete can prolong
OL,12,Frecovery by weakening muscles,
OL,13,Fexposing the person to greater risk of
OL,14,Finfection and generally impacting on
OL,15,Ftheir wellbeing.
OL,17,F"Declaring a BCI is only done when it
OL,18,Fcan help alleviate significant
OL,19,Fpressure. The last time Swansea Bay
OL,20,FUniversity Health Board needed to do
OL,21,Fso was in March 2025.
