OL,7,F"Since then we have streamlined and
OL,8,Freset our urgent and emergency care
OL,9,Fservices, which has significantly
OL,10,Freduced waits for patients and
OL,11,Fambulance handover delays overall."
OL,13,FThe health board added that between
OL,14,FJuly and September 2025, it
OL,15,Fexperienced a 9% increase in
OL,16,Fambulances arriving at its front doors.
OL,18,FOf these, they said an average of 46
OL,19,Fout of 51 patients were handed over to
OL,20,Fhospital in less than 45 minutes -
OL,21,Fequating to a 155% improvement.
